{"tid":1970701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捧習抗疫如孫子用兵 央視被指高級黑","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T01:56:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0996ab547ac33f129947844217572fd515f0dc","tid":1970701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200413/N565SXOUW5HTD75BA3D43O7P4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200413%2FN565SXOUW5HTD75BA3D43O7P4M%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=0fed3028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200413%2FN565SXOUW5HTD75BA3D43O7P4M%2F&h=d6ce6c33\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200413/N565SXOUW5HTD75BA3D43O7P4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n捧習抗疫如孫子用兵 央視被指高級黑<br />\n<br />\n中共喉舌央視近日推出「習近平戰『疫』兵法──知己知彼，百戰不殆」，將習捧為領導抗疫總指揮，詳列疫情以來習「親自指揮、親自部署」種種言論；指習的「很多對策、措施與中國古代兵家思想高度契合」；將習與古代兵家孫子並舉。這是2月中宣部出版《大國戰「疫」》捧習、因反應太差低調下架後，官媒再為習造神。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：20警連續兩晚基隆查牌 凶員工熄爐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200413/large/1586707582_a0f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200413%2Flarge%2F1586707582_a0f8.jpg&h=19ade89f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n央視推出習近平的戰「疫」兵法。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民嘲央視無恥曠古唯一<br />\n<br />\n央視網指疫情爆發後，習「高度重視，始終親自指揮、親自部署」，文章細數抗疫之戰「從遭遇戰到阻擊戰，從重中之重到人民戰爭，從頭等大事到全面勝利」，讚習指揮「這場人民戰爭過程中，很多對策、措施與中國古代兵家思想高度契合」；甚至指病毒基因組排序、新冠病毒疫苗研究等，也在習「兩個親自」下獲進展。<br />\n<br />\n該文將習與古代兵家孫子並舉，堪稱「古有孫子兵法，今有習『戰疫』大法」。網民對央視如此造神感震驚，指「全國人民的痛苦、傷病、勞苦，竟成了習個人的冠冕，個人的功勞」；也有人斥央視「無恥得史無前例、曠古唯一」。更有輿論指，外界對疫情中方做法質疑不斷時，央媒如此給習戴高帽，其實是「高級黑」，將習綁牢在恥辱柱上，接受歷史拷問。<br />\n<br />\n央視網/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"c2da0d791d67694211dd9cb16c2f1f4e1b0e44df","tid":1970701,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"我想問同知己知彼 百戰不殆有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是但撻句野出黎就鳩嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9319070cd31946ecb16cbec80f484941858b89e","tid":1970701,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"知道武漢肺炎有幾毒所以用黎殺全球人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e494e5a1a43fdfcc317c1fce8f7efbbd66fd732","tid":1970701,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"寫本書個人都幾慘<br />\n要將甴曱平講過既野係兵法搵個相應既句子<br />\n真係勇氣毅力可嘉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e50dee66527e9c7ef802436e34ea285bd31ce90","tid":1970701,"uid":30247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2da0d791d67694211dd9cb16c2f1f4e1b0e44df","tid":1970701,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"我想問同知己知彼 百戰不殆有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是但撻句野出黎就鳩嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"可能暗示緊隻病毒係自己整出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b62efe6d796102fccd78276a694b78e1450023a","tid":1970701,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e50dee66527e9c7ef802436e34ea285bd31ce90","tid":1970701,"uid":30247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2da0d791d67694211dd9cb16c2f1f4e1b0e44df","tid":1970701,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"我想問同知己知彼 百戰不殆有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是但撻句野出黎就鳩嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"可